title: Status Cleaner 1.0 [Cracked]
description:
## App Name : Status Cleaner 1.0 [Cracked]
## Released : Jan 08, 2014
## Version  : 1.0
## Size     : 0.7 MB
## Language : English


For more or to buy from the Official Apple Mac App Store : 






## Description :


Make your iOS screenshots perfect, by cleaning up messy status bars with Status Cleaner.

Status Cleaner allows you to easily adjust the appearance of the status bar in your final production screenshots. Set signal strength, Wi-Fi on/off, centre text (time) and more.

Supports individual and batch processing of retina screenshots for both iPhone and iPad.
